        <div class="span12 well">
@*            <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert">×</button>*@
            <p>
                Every card in your library has a card level ranging from 0 to 5.  This level indicates the number of times you have consecutively answered the card correctly.
            </p>
            <p>
                When you first create a card it will be at level 0.  If you answer the card correctly in your quiz it will move to level 1 and so on.  If you answer the card incorrectly, regardless of the level it is currently on, it will return back to level 0.
            </p>
            <p>
                Each card level has a value associated with it indicating the number of days before the card will be asked in your daily quiz again.
            </p>
        </div>
