    <div class="row-fluid skip-line">
        <div class="span10 offset1">
            <h4>Use the sliders below to set the number of days a card should wait before appearing in your quiz again.</h4>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row-fluid skip-line">
        <div class="span10 offset1">
            <span>
                When a card is <span class="strong">first created</span> it should be asked in the quiz after 
                <input type="text" class="strong input-mini right-text-align level-slider-label" data-bind="value: userConfiguration().quizInterval0, valueUpdate: 'afterkeydown'" /> <span data-bind="html: userConfiguration().quizInterval0DayLabel"></span>
            </span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="span10 offset1">
